# Project Structure

> This document defines mandatory project conventions.
> These rules apply to both human contributors and AI-generated code.

## Always on

These rules apply to all code organization and structure decisions.

### Directory Layout

- `src/dispatchbox/` - Source code
  - `cli.py` - Command-line interface
  - `config.py` - Configuration constants
  - `handlers.py` - Event handlers
  - `http_server.py` - HTTP server for health checks and API
  - `models.py` - Data models (OutboxEvent)
  - `repository.py` - Database repository
  - `supervisor.py` - Process supervision
  - `worker.py` - Worker implementation
- `tests/` - Test files
- `docs/` - Documentation
- `scripts/` - Utility scripts
- `sql/` - SQL scripts

### Import Style

- Use absolute imports from `dispatchbox`
- Group imports: standard library, third-party, local
